column8: Hello, indeed. Hold it right there.
Charon, sir... have anything to listen to along the way?
Zagreus? Come here a moment, please.
I'm going to miss you too, Son.
It's not so bad, Son. I agree with that.
So good to see you, Son.
Good to be back at last.
I know how mortals hate waiting around!
I knew you could do it.
I can always count on you.
Sounds good. I'll see you then.
